metadata.name: Sho
metadata.description:
Sho Kusakabe is the brother of the Fire Force's protagonist, Shinra. Raised by the White-Clad with a strong connection to the Evangelist’s grace, Sho is one of the few Adolla Burst users in the series.

Adolla is a “pure and unsullied” flame from another dimension. Individuals connected to this flame possess otherworldly powers. Sho Kusakabe can bend time and space to his will, making him almost invincible in battle.
